name: Bearspawn #1 [Alternate]
description:
The origin of the classic, the original Bear that went to hell for love, and was revived after a hibernation to become a Bearspawn, part bear, part demon, destined to lead the forces of Bear hell against Bear Heaven. 

Own this gorgeous token commemorating Bearspawn #1 Alternate "Masked cover" Exploring what it would look like if bears wore masks.
